OL,6,FThe defendant, of Tamworth Road,
OL,7,FTamworth, could also be heard shouting
OL,8,F"f****** paedos" towards the hotel and
OL,9,Ftelling police officers to "f*** off".
OL,11,FSentencing him at Stafford Crown
OL,12,FCourt, Judge John Edwards told Jordan:
OL,13,F"You rightly hung your head in shame
OL,14,Fas we watched the video.
OL,16,F"I have looked with care at the
OL,17,Ffootage, you are front and centre of
OL,18,Fthis baying mob for an hour-and-a-
OL,19,Fhalf."
